name: Absolute Beginners
overview: Two childhood best friends enjoying their final seaside summer as they prepare for film school meet an aspiring athlete who ignites unfamiliar desires.

episodes.name: Episode 1

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Despite Igor's dismay following the beach encounter, Lena hatches a scheme to mend ties. Tamara's plan to move abroad strains Niko's family dynamic.

episodes.name: Episode 3

episodes.name: Episode 4
